• Chronic truancy: habitual truancy (a minimum of 20 days
within a school year) without a legitimate reason
<table>
<tr><td>
<p>
? Another example is the situation in which children who are
supposed to be home schooled are obviously not being
provided an education at home.
</p>
</td></tr>
</table>


? Another example is the situation in which children who are
supposed to be home schooled are obviously not being
