abused adolescents. In J. Briere, L. Berliner, J. Bulkley, C. Jenny, &amp;
T. Reid (Eds.), <i>The APSAC handbook on child maltreatment</i> (pp. 119-139).
Thousand Oaks, CA: Sage.


