[p. <i>[172]</i>] | [<a href="psyc.get.jpg.aspx?display=page&amp;legacyid=1000334627-I00192&amp;api=new&amp;maxwidth=700">Page Image</a>]<br />
[p. <i>[173]</i>] | [<a href="psyc.get.jpg.aspx?display=page&amp;legacyid=1000334627-I00193&amp;api=new&amp;maxwidth=700">Page Image</a>]<br />
[p. <i>[174]</i>] | [<a href="psyc.get.jpg.aspx?display=page&amp;legacyid=1000334627-I00194&amp;api=new&amp;maxwidth=700">Page Image</a>]<br />
