[p. <i>187</i>] | [<a href="psyc.get.jpg.aspx?display=page&amp;legacyid=1000334627-I00207&amp;api=new&amp;maxwidth=700">Page Image</a>]<br />

Freidrich, W. N., Grambsch, P., Damon, L. Hewitt, S., Koverola, C.
Lang, R., Wolfe, V. &amp; Broughton, D. (1992). Child sexual behavior
inventory: Normative and clinical comparisons. <i>Psychological Assessment,
4</i>(3), 303-311.


Horton, C. (1996). Children who molest other children: The school
psychologist's response to the sexually aggressive child. <i>School Psychology
